LACHMAN / Los Angeles Times; Photo, (A2) Saints March In: New Orleans rallied 
with two fourth-quarter touchdowns to beat the Rams, 24-20. Saint Gill Fenerty, 
who scored on a 60-yard run, gains short yardage on this play. ; Photo, Henry 
