demonstrated near New York's St. Patrick's Cathedral -- a quiet day compared to 
a year ago, when 4,500 gathered to protest church teachings and 113 were 
arrested. This year, the archdiocese got a court order to keep protesters from 
disrupting services. Four were arrested. Reuters 
</P>
