<TEXT>
<P>
An explosion ripped through a Soviet petrochemical plant in the Siberian city 
of Tomsk on Sunday, injuring an unknown number of people, the official Tass 
news agency said. 
</P>
<P>
The explosion occurred when workers started up a section producing ethylene 
just after midday. The agency gave no other details. 
